Mods, you need to mod.  If you think someone is just here to start shit and disrupt the forum, ban them.  If you think someone is just a little clueless and essentially harmless, warn them, then if you need to ,ban them.  People were chosen because someone trusts your judgment in character.  You guys are smart enough to figure out who needs to go and who should stay.  You don't need tons of rules and polls to do your jobs.<br>
<br>
Modding the forum is about more then creating superfluous sections and adding new emoticons. <br>
